<p begin="00:00:00.800" end="00:00:06.150" style="s2">hi my name is Joe Brewer and I&#39;m the</p>
<p begin="00:00:03.810" end="00:00:07.859" style="s2">director of cognitive policy works and</p>
<p begin="00:00:06.150" end="00:00:09.360" style="s2">i&#39;m here to share with you a project</p>
<p begin="00:00:07.859" end="00:00:12.990" style="s2">that we&#39;ve decided to initiate in</p>
<p begin="00:00:09.360" end="00:00:16.020" style="s2">partnership with darwin SF to help get</p>
<p begin="00:00:12.990" end="00:00:19.199" style="s2">the global culture to a tipping point or</p>
<p begin="00:00:16.020" end="00:00:21.090" style="s2">we can finally tackle climate change now</p>
