<p begin="00:00:21.090" end="00:00:24.689" style="s2">years ago i was studying atmospheric</p>
<p begin="00:00:22.949" end="00:00:26.180" style="s2">science in graduate school and i</p>
<p begin="00:00:24.689" end="00:00:29.580" style="s2">realized that the biggest problem</p>
