<p begin="00:01:17.580" end="00:01:21.540" style="s2">droughts extreme weather like hurricane</p>
<p begin="00:01:19.770" end="00:01:24.420" style="s2">sandy bearing down on New York City</p>
<p begin="00:01:21.540" end="00:01:27.450" style="s2">earlier this month and still even in</p>
<p begin="00:01:24.420" end="00:01:29.729" style="s2">spite of that the massive PR campaign</p>
